<p>
The Master’s Degree Program in Applied Mathematics at Ryerson University began in Fall 2009. Our graduate students receive a solid education in 
Applied Mathematics which prepares them to pursue successful careers in industry and academia. Given the low ratio of students to faculty members, a 
distinguished characteristic of our program is the dedicated attention that students receive during their studies.
These pages will try to provide you with useful information on the structure of the program, how to apply, and the Department of Mathematics itself.
</p> 



 <p>
<table style align="center">
	
<tr>
<th>&nbsp;&nbsp;Masters</th>
<th>&nbsp;&nbsp;PhD</th>
</tr>

