<p>
<img src="FOS open house.png" alt="FOS Open House" width="590" height="288">
</P>

<p>
Join the <strong> Faculty of Science Virtual Graduate Open House</strong> to learn more about the research opportunities offered at Ryerson University, students support and admission process.
</p>

<p>
Graduate programs participating:
<br><i>Applied Mathematics - MSc.</i>
<br><i>Mathematical Modelling and Methods - Ph.D.</i>
<br><i>Molecular Science (Chemistry and Biology Department) - MSc and Ph.D.</i>
<br><i>Physics - MSc. and Ph.D.</i>
</P>

<p>
There will be a few presentations followed by <strong>breakout sessions for each graduate program.</strong>
</p>

<p>
Presenters:
<br><a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/physics/our-people/michael-kolios/">Michael Kolios</a>, Associate Dean Research and Graduate Studies, Faculty of Science
<br><a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/physics/our-people/carl-kumaradas/">Carl Kumaradas</a>, Associate Dean, Programs, Yeates School of Graduate Studies
<br>Aina Arro, Admissions Officer, Yeates School of Graduate Studies
<br>Camara Chambers, Senior Manager, Career Education, Career & Co-op Centre
</p>

<p>
Register at: <a href="http://bit.ly/FOSgradOpenHouse">bit.ly/FOSgradOpenHouse
</a>
</p>

<p>
We look forward to seeing you there!

</p>

